{"id":340996,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":1,"day":21}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"150","ytitle":"","mtitle":"赠艾德林","ftitle":"——并题白石老人画","authors":["艾青"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开了一幅一幅的画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像打开一年最好的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，房子外面是冬天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面是夏天的水果、春天的花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日葵、牡丹、荔枝和枇把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草边的青蛙、水中的蝦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有熟透了的樱桃的甜味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振动翅膀的蜜蜂的嗡鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿是一串朱红的小鱼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孕育、生长在自由中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿世界能持久和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切美好的都得到繁荣19574年1月，北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1957\\01\\571l030101.JPG\">"}]}